{"tid":1775732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一天光晒 走出婚變危機 洪欣同老公湊西女兒終於識笑","createTime":"2019-12-09T04:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T07:18:10.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9daa189db8443f703e7ed42ca631cb07002fcd72","tid":1775732,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"49歲洪欣和38歲的老公張丹峰結婚10年，去年7月男方被爆與經理人畢瀅過從甚密而鬧出緋聞，當時洪欣對老公表示信任，強調清楚知道兩人只是工作關係，但有消息指今年農曆新年期間，洪欣到重慶探張丹峰班送驚喜，卻發現老公同畢瀅共處酒店房，關係古怪令她拂袖而去，隨即傳出婚變。今年六月，兩公婆一齊去澳門睇已成內地組合「新風暴」成員的兒子張鎬濂開騷，表現一般，應該又係同簽咗約，但無諗住會捧紅佢哋。有指張丹峰一直為「偷食風波」努力箍煲，送車又報行蹤，總算○氹番有米老婆！上周二，兩公婆帶埋5歲囡囡同女友人及另外三個小朋友去銅鑼灣shopping，張丹峰全程陪住太太睇首飾又護實個女好體貼，最難得見到素顏的洪欣終於識笑，咁咪好囉。 採訪：打工仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/udooph6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fudooph6.jpg&h=3e82b461&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bqujRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bqujRv.jpg&h=35ce63cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ButvOKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FButvOKT.jpg&h=817356e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff03bb61d5ecb9b487b3c24b64908e0e2d566ed1","tid":1775732,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQuiXDt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQuiXDt.jpg&h=e1368802&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e29049a54705abe513be19fa8c2679e5f2deff7","tid":1775732,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vS3jG5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvS3jG5f.jpg&h=2cdb0da4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c41aef900aa59b5428b44873389ae746eed593c5","tid":1775732,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e29049a54705abe513be19fa8c2679e5f2deff7","tid":1775732,"uid":48905,"like":